    "body": "I had a quick look and search and found this: https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/1015\r\n\r\nIs it still relevant?\r\n\r\nThe searchbox code is brittle because we tried to make it a bit of a component and a bit of a connector early on (lot of cases/customization), any change to it could break other things sadly..\r\n\r\nLet me know what you think.",
