    "body": "Works like a charm 👍 \r\n\r\nI dont think it adresses the same issue @vvo from what I've read, the state isn't updated until the search is performed. So it won't still be able to perform a search from an external button without \"hack\" and getting the value from the input with JavaScript. Did I understood it correctly @bobylito ?",
